message: Frank Sabella, a detective at the Cumberland County Prosecutor’s Office, said human trafficking in this region could look like anything from farm labor to a domestic violence situation where a man might force a woman into sex work to support a mutual drug habit. #NewJersey #LawEnforcement #EndHumanTrafficking

data.description: The death last month of accused trafficker Jeffrey Epstein is just a public example of how justice is delayed, or nonexistent, for victims of human
data.title: In the world of sex trafficking, justice is hard to find
